title: Autodesk AutoCAD 2010
description:
- make sure that .NET Framework Runtime 3.5 SP1 is installed (otherwise ACAD will crash)!
- make sure DirectX 9.0 Runtime is installed!
- serial-number: 000-00000000
- click on the configure button
- select stand-alone license and click next
- select custom and deselect marterial library, samples and tutorials
- click "Configuration Complete" instead of "Next" now!
- click install
- setup can't find several help and doc files, ignore errors!
- after install, copy adlmint.dll from EQX to your installed dir



NOTE: if you used acad as trial and didn't copy the crack before the first start the product license information (about) shows an expiration date but you can ignore that....
